{"tid":2407504,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"情人節合體丨孫藝珍冧爆講I do 甜笑拍打玄彬胸口","createTime":"2021-02-14T05:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T07:28:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3512ff89dad566701ac2cc374223d8979c8122","tid":2407504,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NSd7FNjLOVXKW0b--39yQQFMRB8=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QIUDCYEZGNFWDIK2H2PKO3YV2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNSd7FNjLOVXKW0b--39yQQFMRB8%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQIUDCYEZGNFWDIK2H2PKO3YV2E.jpg&h=56780428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人氣韓劇《愛的迫降》的玄彬及孫藝珍，今年元旦日終於承認戀情，據當時報道指兩人已拍拖8個月。今日情人節，是兩人認戀後首個度過的情人節，雖然未知兩人如何慶祝，但廣告商就非常有心，於今日公開兩人的廣告，令元旦情侶成功在今日情人節合體。<br />\n<br />\nFans大呼驚喜<br />\n兩人早前因為《愛的迫降》帶挈爆紅，更令他們以情侶檔擔任菲律賓的電訊公司任代言人，齊齊搵銀。由於當時拍攝廣告時兩人仍未公開戀情，而且之前廣告商公開的廣告都是兩人各自拍攝的場面，直到今日情人節，廣告商就非常識做公開兩人一齊的廣告片，令fans大呼驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n拍廣告兼耍花槍<br />\n於廣告中，玄彬駕駛跑車去搵孫藝珍，不過兩人疑似在不同空間，一直未能遇上。而畫面亦出現《愛的迫降》的片段，之後兩人終於遇上，玄彬以英文問：「Do you believe this is possible？（你認為這有可能嗎？）」孫藝珍即冧爆表示：「I do.」孫藝珍更甜笑地雙手輕輕拍打玄彬胸口，似乎當時兩人邊拍廣告邊耍花槍，sweet到漏油。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YaaLdXF2luKu60NYOG31chXxE4k=/802x449/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S5OKUIA4PJDDTK4I345EBELWUY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYaaLdXF2luKu60NYOG31chXxE4k%3D%2F802x449%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS5OKUIA4PJDDTK4I345EBELWUY.JPG&h=5f59b339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NyAEyg3kU4C8mvY91KKPADqsehk=/802x445/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GN5ZBAHO2VDSNAWYGUDWFPNDMY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNyAEyg3kU4C8mvY91KKPADqsehk%3D%2F802x445%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGN5ZBAHO2VDSNAWYGUDWFPNDMY.JPG&h=fa9919bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ISpRrxLntR5_BZLPXL9lLlaL8Ls=/802x384/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NWLBQPZGZZFVLKKOOUNDXLATVA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FISpRrxLntR5_BZLPXL9lLlaL8Ls%3D%2F802x384%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNWLBQPZGZZFVLKKOOUNDXLATVA.JPG&h=55346cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Yoq2l0o5Mztzr8uGOugbB7OvckU=/802x393/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3SRJ42UVSFFFHEXCR6A3EG3NRI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYoq2l0o5Mztzr8uGOugbB7OvckU%3D%2F802x393%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3SRJ42UVSFFFHEXCR6A3EG3NRI.JPG&h=629a339a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SI-zFugtW3qOFhlJvUOJwu3Lj7Q=/802x398/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V5LY6DUNL5GEZOQQSWHFAWYH3A.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSI-zFugtW3qOFhlJvUOJwu3Lj7Q%3D%2F802x398%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV5LY6DUNL5GEZOQQSWHFAWYH3A.JPG&h=b6ecc0d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/edLAxwyhNEC0WqKmt4qdOS0KEww=/802x470/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TAY